      "writtenOn": "2021-02-16T21:47:13Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think Filter types is more important than filter syntax. I think we should move this section on top.\n\nAnd perhaps we should reword \"Filter Syntax\" to \"Advanced Syntax\"?, and only cover the advanced type (i.e. remove line 88)?",
      "revId": "167cad791f5c4ec5fa7ebbd5ff1bdc903f40ba3a",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba"
